Виды патронов:
Round <- Bullet <- Casing(cartridge) 
  I) Shotgun Shell 
  II) Rifle Round
  III) Pistol Round 

Examples of calibers:
  Малые калибры:
    .22 Long Rifle(LR) - small, used in small guns(22 дюйма), 100-150 J
    .25 ACP - used in mini-pistols(Colt 1908), 80-100 J
  Средние калибры:
    9 mm Parabellum - used in most handguns(Makarov, Glock 17, Beretta 92), very balanced, 500-600 J
    .380 ACP (9×17 мм Short) - compact pistols(Walther PPK, Bersa Thunder), 300 J
    .40 S&W - wall breaking, 

